{"comments":"TypeRole — semantic purpose of text in a design system.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nTypeRole goes beyond hierarchy levels (H1-H6) to describe the\nsemantic PURPOSE of text. This enables:\n\n- Consistent styling by meaning, not just size\n- Accessibility (screen readers, semantic HTML)\n- Design system token mapping\n- Intent-driven typography\n\n## Role Categories\n\n**Display**: Large, attention-grabbing text\n- Hero, Display, Title, Subtitle\n\n**Content**: Reading and body text\n- Body, BodyLarge, BodySmall, Lead\n\n**UI**: Interface text\n- Label, Button, Input, Link, Navigation\n\n**Supporting**: Metadata and supplementary\n- Caption, Helper, Error, Success, Warning\n\n**Code**: Technical text\n- Code, CodeBlock, PreFormatted\n\n## Dependencies\n\nNone — this is a pure enumeration type.\n\n## Dependents\n\n- TypeStyle (role-based styling)\n- Theme (semantic token mapping)\n- Accessibility (ARIA roles)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[95,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TypeRole.purs","start":[95,3]},"title":"Hero"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[96,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TypeRole.purs","start":[96,3]},"title":"Display"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[97,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TypeRole.purs","start":[97,3]},"title":"Title"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[98,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TypeRole.purs","start":[98,3]},"title":"Subtitle"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[101,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TypeRole.purs","start":[101,3]},"title":"Lead"},{"comments":null,"info":{"argumen